Reasoning: The paper discusses an algorithm for computing the homotopic \Frechet distance between two polygonal curves, which involves computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph algorithms (cs.DS). The curves are on the boundary of a triangulated topological disk, which falls under computational topology (cs.GR). The paper also mentions a $O(\log n)$-approximation algorithm, which involves approximation algorithms (cs.DM) and complexity theory (cs.CC).
